{"tid":2514226,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"721白衣人暴動案 8被告6月18日裁決","createTime":"2021-05-03T06:25:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T06:44:41.000Z","uid":147376,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0cf8d26044dcf27c87150a75a2a7ac2678ffec33","tid":2514226,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T06:25:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.881903.com/news/amp/local/2389258\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Famp%2Flocal%2F2389258&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOID442Ur5281Gkz3GsmHlD8%3D&h=07eab892\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.881903.com/news/amp/local/2389258</a><br />\n<br />\n721元朗暴動案今日在區域法院結案陳詞，6名被告否認控罪，法官將案件押後至6月18日裁決。控辯雙方早前已經提交書面陳詞，法官葉佐文質疑，控方就有意圖傷人的控罪，各被告的角色及涉及的行為，其中第二被告只是指罵他人，是否都是意圖傷人。控方指，被告的指罵行為鼓勵他人施襲，根據共同犯罪原則，屬於主要參與者，或次要參與者；辯方稱，次被告只涉及「罵」人的行為，不足以證明其意圖。<br />\n案中8名被告，其中兩人早前已承認暴動罪，另外六名被告分別被控暴動罪、有意圖而傷人罪及串謀有意圖傷人罪。"},{"pid":"f5644baeee3127525719d56dc047e96a6fd4ec27","tid":2514226,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T06:25:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"81ea0f7179a5225ab0f746d0d742f94a85cc46fa","tid":2514226,"uid":174013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T06:36:40.000Z","msg":"等睇得認罪果兩件要坐"},{"pid":"afe23986e1a0b98b2b8c3b6f5a26e7dea7a22c83","tid":2514226,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"81ea0f7179a5225ab0f746d0d742f94a85cc46fa","tid":2514226,"uid":174013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T06:36:40.000Z","msg":"等睇得認罪果兩件要坐"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T06:39:13.000Z","msg":"其實其餘嗰啲有曬片都好難走得甩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e860fd0ac6168cc307145074031c4cf969c5cbd","tid":2514226,"uid":47311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"afe23986e1a0b98b2b8c3b6f5a26e7dea7a22c83","tid":2514226,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"